name: James Webb
description: I am a young heart with open mind, someone who accepts people as they are and what l want then to be, I am a fair individual who adapts to changes in life and enjoys life to the fullest. I’m what friend will say honest and most trustworthy, I seek that in a mate, someone who is compassionate,romantic,loving yet understanding who has a calm demeanor and a great personality. I love to travel and would love to meet someone who shares all her love with me till her rest of our life, fun and adventure. I am stress free and fun to be around, I love to laugh and I am also a great cook who enjoys a variety of foods. I am an avid reader and a great conservationist. I also like to have social functions and entertain friends. I am a very private person who enjoys the comforts of home relaxing and listening to good music, I also love Jazz,rock and the Opera. Lots more to my profile but I am sure you will be intrigued to know the rest…
